data.description: Prime location near the heart of downtown York! A charming covered front porch welcomes you, providing a cozy spot to relax. This home features an open floor plan and neutral paint and finishes allow you to personalize the space with your own unique style. Storage won't be an issue with three generously sized walk-in closets. Low maintenance LVP flooring throughout. Don't miss the opportunity to make this downtown gem your own – a perfect blend of convenience, charm, and comfort awaits you in this prime York location!
